Split licensing model for this repository:

- compiler source, tests, docs, examples, and scripts are licensed under
  GPL-3.0-or-later
- public headers and runtime material intended for compiled firmware are
  licensed under GPL-3.0-or-later WITH GCC-exception-3.1

License texts:

- COPYING contains the full GNU General Public License version 3 text
- COPYING.RUNTIME contains the full GCC Runtime Library Exception version 3.1 text
